INSERT INTO public.tojung (id,num,total,jan,feb,mar,apr,may,jun,jul,aug,sep,oct,nov,"dec",created_at,nation) VALUES (345,'047','✨ 1. 2026 Overall Fortune
The year 2026 requires patience and prudence. Like the sun setting in the west, dark times may come temporarily, but just as there is roundness within angular things, hope will surely appear after difficulties. Even if there is fame and profit, gossip may follow, so be careful with words and act humbly. Don''t jump into troublesome matters and invite trouble; exercise self-restraint and wisdom to wait for the right time. Rather than rushing hastily, proceeding calmly and sincerely will eventually bring good results.

