This is a year requiring caution and patience at work. In the first half, don''t expand greatly or rush, and be faithful to current duties. In April and May, difficulties may arise from disagreements between parties, so strive for harmony and communication. In July, gossip may actually lead to good results, so don''t be afraid. In October and November, you can see the fruits of steady effort. Judge job changes or startups carefully, and postpone until next year if possible.

